{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"14201692e2","title":"湖南秋收暴动要有军队帮助","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"36428a70aa","index":0,"year":1927,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"14201692e2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"78ee7f7425","type":"paragraph","text":"湖南秋收暴动要有军队帮助！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"14201692e2"},{"id":"8c26a3c024","type":"paragraph","text":"（1927年8月18日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"14201692e2"},{"id":"3cb2ae8395","type":"paragraph","text":"一、湖南的秋收暴动的发展，是解决农民的土地问题，这是谁都不能否认的。但要来制造这个暴动，要发动暴动，单靠农民的力量是不行的，必须有一个军事的帮助。有一两团兵力，这个暴动就可起来，否则终归于失败。二、暴动的发展是要夺取政权，要夺取政权，没有兵力的拥卫去夺取，这是自欺的话。我们党从前的错误，就是忽略了军事，现在应以百分之六十的精力注意军事运动，实行在枪杆上夺取政权，建设政权","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"14201692e2"},{"id":"c5ec0485af","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和易礼容在改组后的中共湖南省委第一次会议上讨论湖","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"14201692e2"}],"page":{"id":"7b8cc6691c","publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"14201692e2","start":65,"end":65}}}},"__N_SSG":true}